Exactly--Deviation got it. The Nostromo was a tug, towing a giant refinery. The Sulaco was a troop transport. While at least a certain amount of the fancy-futuristicness of Prometheus is going to be because the movie is newer, it's also got a lot to do with it being a privately-funded science expedition with the absolute highest of high-tech gizmos.
